      "comment": "ITCHY'S FLYER (2) was in the minors two back (18.92) at this track but ran below best last time at Goulburn, finishing 8th. Has a good record here at this journey. Has ability and is a key runner. LOLA MCGRAW (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.90) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can do much better this time. TIMBER JACK (8) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 318m behind One Last Shot (18.96) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Worth following up. MAHOME GIRL (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
